=== Approved_VPNs ===
"We'll only allow approved government and corporate VPNs!" # diagram: two_tier_internet.jpg

This creates a two-tier system. Businesses get secure connections. Individuals face restrictions.

"Approved" VPNs require:
• Government visibility into connections
• Cooperation with authority requests
• Approval that can be revoked

The system still fails because kids can use parent's work VPNs or older sibling's accounts.

